---
description: React components—forms, tables, layout, Tailwind, shadcn, empty/loading states
globs: src/components/**/*.tsx
alwaysApply: false
---

# UI primitives

- Import shadcn from `@/components/ui/...` only. Never hand-edit `src/components/ui/**`.
- Use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` for conditional classes.
- Icons: `lucide-react` only, per-icon imports, size with `size-4` / `size-5` / `size-8` etc.

# Layout patterns

- Page: `flex flex-1 flex-col gap-4 p-4`
- Page header: `flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4`
- Page title: `text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl`
- Table shell: `overflow-hidden rounded-md border`
- Stat grids: `grid grid-cols-1 divide-y rounded-md border md:grid-cols-N md:divide-x md:divide-y-0`

# RTL / i18n-aware layout

- Locales: `en-US` (LTR), `ar-SA` (RTL). Prefer logical Tailwind (`ms-*`, `me-*`, `ps-*`, `pe-*`, `border-s`, `border-e`); use `rtl:` / `ltr:` when required.
- Sidebar placement follows existing `_app` behavior.

# Forms (RHF + Zod)

- `useForm` with `zodResolver` and `<Feature>Schema` / `SchemaInitData` from services.
- `shouldUnregister: true` when fields mount/unmount.
- Fields: `<Controller>` + shadcn `Field` / `FieldLabel` / `FieldDescription` / `FieldError`; `data-invalid` on `Field`; `aria-invalid` on control; `disabled={loading}` during mutations; ids `feature-field` kebab-case.
- Do not use `register` directly for shadcn-style controls.
- Select / Switch / Calendar / Popover / Command: explicit `value` + `onValueChange`.
- Submit: create → `disabled={loading || !form.formState.isValid}`; update → also require `form.formState.isDirty`.
- Dialog create: reset on `DialogContent` `onCloseAutoFocus`. Dialog edit: `useEffect` + `form.reset(data, { keepDefaultValues: false })` when entity loads; do **not** reset on `onOpenChange` only.

# Tables (TanStack Table)

- Decompose only as far as similar features do (`Table`, `TableMain`, `TableColumnDefs`, search/filter/pagination/export/delete/reset when needed). Card-backed collections may add a `<Feature>Card.tsx` and omit unused table subpieces.
- Owner file holds query hook, `columnFilters`, optional `columnVisibility`, optional `rowSelection`, `useReactTable`, toolbar, wrapper, and pagination only when exposed by the UI.
- Settings aligned with existing tables: `pageSize: 20`, `autoResetPageIndex: false`, stable `getRowId` (`row._id as string` for database entities, `row.clerkId` for access grants), `getCoreRowModel`, `getFilteredRowModel`, and `getPaginationRowModel` when pagination is enabled.
- Loading: `TableSkeleton` for literal table views; feature/card skeletons for card or grid collections. Empty table body: `t("no-results")`; card/grid collections may use a feature-specific empty key such as `t("no-access-found")`.
- Columns fn returns `ColumnDef[]`; first column select checkbox when the feature uses row selection; last column actions when row actions live in a table; short cell renderers; small in-file header components for translations. Headless filtering columns can be accessor-only.
- Export: feature helpers + PapaParse + UTF-8 BOM; filenames `${feature}_${Date.now()}.csv` or `.json` per existing exporters.

# Empty / error / loading

- Order early returns: missing scope → empty component → loading skeletons → `GenericError` → content.
- Empty/error components live in `components/empty-states` using shadcn `Empty` building blocks.
- Section query errors: `GenericError`; do not show raw API strings on pages.
- Router-level errors: shared `ErrorComponent` pattern from `empty-states`.

# Theme

- Use `ThemeProvider` / patterns from `contexts/theme-provider` (`vite-ui-theme` storage) unless changing theme architecture.
